title: 820-00165-A Board no Light on Magsafe
message: 820-00165-A Board no Light on Magsafe, does have light sometimes but most of the time does not. Everything else on machine works perfectly fine, using known good charger. Any idea?

title: 820-00165-A Board no Light on Magsafe
message:
Try known good LIO board and flex.
Also inspect LIO connector from MLB.
Check continuity for SYS_ONEWIRE from MLB to the LIO board; onewire circuit in LIO board is very easy to locate...
